        {
            "title": "微軟與OpenAI合作關係轉為非獨家,股價下跌2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mRIbnRh2Dbe.RQV4qwcOHg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC4G11Q_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"微軟\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:微軟;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/微軟\">微軟</a>(NASDAQ:MSFT)股價週一下跌2%,而亞馬遜(NASDAQ:AMZN)上漲1%,此前OpenAI宣布與<span><span><span><span>微軟</span></span></span></span>的授權協議將轉為非獨家。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">兩家公司披露了一項修訂後的合作協議,該協議取消了微軟對OpenAI知識產權的獨家權利。根據新條款,微軟將保留對OpenAI模型和產品的授權至2032年,但該授權現在將變為非獨家,允許OpenAI向其他合作夥伴授權其技術。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">修訂後的協議還取消了微軟向OpenAI支付的收入分成,儘管OpenAI將繼續向微軟支付收入分成至2030年,分成比例保持不變,但設有總額上限。這些付款將繼續進行,與OpenAI的技術進展無關。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-666e3087-5a6f-329a-a73a-b8a8055f7a30-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">微軟將繼續擔任OpenAI的主要雲端合作夥伴,除非微軟無法或選擇不支持必要的功能,否則OpenAI產品將首先在Azure上發布。然而,OpenAI現在可以通過任何雲端服務提供商向客戶提供其所有產品,這標誌著與先前獨家安排的重大轉變。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">兩家公司表示,修訂後的協議為雙方提供了長期的明確性和靈活性,使其能夠在追求新機會的同時,繼續在數據中心容量、下一代晶片和網絡安全人工智能應用方面進行合作。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據新條款,微軟作為主要股東繼續參與OpenAI的增長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BE%AE%E8%BB%9F%E8%88%87openai%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82%E8%BD%89%E7%82%BA%E9%9D%9E%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6-%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C2-141041440.html",
