            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "Mizuho上調CrowdStrike評級、下調Adobe評級 AI策略分歧顯現",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GQcDb8ntU.u8og0ujZxDlw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEAB20CL_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - Mizuho分析師Gregg Moskowitz週一做出兩項相反的評級調整,將CrowdStrike上調至跑贏大盤,同時將Adobe下調至中性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些調整反映出兩家公司在AI領域發展前景的分歧。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對於CrowdStrike,Mizuho將目標價從490美元上調至520美元,理由是該平台需求強勁,且當前估值下風險/回報比具吸引力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司指出了幾個增長驅動因素,包括Falcon Flex、超大規模雲端市場和AI安全計劃,並補充說\"完全預期CRWD將充分利用AI安全領域的機會\",並認為該公司\"可以說擁有該領域最強大的產品組合\"。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-119d033f-1ca3-38ea-bba6-274a7c6b23c6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Mizuho還將Project Glasswing視為潛在催化劑,認為\"Project Glasswing很有可能隨著時間推移為CRWD帶來良好的增量業務活動\"。該公司股票目前交易價格約為2027年度ARR的14倍,該機構稱這一估值\"更為合理\",風險回報比有利。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對於<span><span>Adobe</span></span>,Mizuho將目標價從315美元下調至270美元,理由是專業消費者和中小企業市場競爭加劇,且\"股票缺乏明確的催化劑\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該機構警告存在\"利潤率下滑的風險\",並表示現在認為Adobe未來兩到三年的有機收入和ARR複合年增長率\"最多只能達到高個位數\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Moskowitz承認推遲下調評級的時間過長,指出該機構\"錯誤地推遲了下調評級,儘管當時估值看起來很有吸引力\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"我們認為從目前來看,ADBE的風險/回報狀況大致平衡,\"他總結道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/mizuho%E4%B8%8A%E8%AA%BFcrowdstrike%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BFadobe%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-ai%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E5%88%86%E6%AD%A7%E9%A1%AF%E7%8F%BE-124544157.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-27 21:07:18",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "Yardeni:3月30日低點為今年股市底部",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cnuI5Tv_0wsbw9g616LjUQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/asian_3_M_1440047966.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - Yardeni Research認為美國股市最糟糕的時期已經過去,宣稱3月30日的低點標誌著今年股市的底部,並重申標普500指數年底目標為7,700點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司將當前形勢與1956年蘇伊士運河危機進行了歷史類比,當時運河關閉導致原油價格大幅上漲,道瓊工業平均指數下跌約10%,但隨後在次年春季回升至新高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Yardeni寫道:\"除了1970年代之外,地緣政治石油供應衝擊往往是股市的買入機會。\"</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b8600e2c-448c-3e99-a418-3a0d61c9205f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗對霍爾木茲海峽的封鎖以及美國對伊朗港口的封鎖仍在持續,週末在伊斯蘭堡舉行的和平談判未能取得成果。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Yardeni的基本情境預測\"標普500指數將在僵局持續期間於7,000點附近震盪,然後在今年下半年逐步走高\"至7,700點目標,前提是年中達成協議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司指出,強勁的盈利表現支撐了看漲前景。標普500指數遠期每股盈利上週創下344.30美元的新高紀錄,2026年的共識預估為326.78美元,2027年為380.37美元,兩者均持續被上調。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Yardeni還指出,目前標普500指數成分股中有82.6%顯示正向遠期盈利增長,今年稍後廣度可能達到90%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在信貸方面,商業銀行貸款和租賃年增7.1%,為近三年來最快增速,Yardeni將此視為不預期出現經濟衰退的關鍵原因。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
